As an AI language model, I do not have personal experiences but I will provide you with three ways on how to make money:

1. Earn money through a job or career: This includes finding a full-time or part-time job in a specific industry or working from home as a freelancer. By gaining experience, building skills, and working hard, you can earn a steady income to support yourself.

2. Invest in stocks or real estate: Investing in stocks or real estate can help you earn passive income. By buying stocks or investing in property, you can earn dividends, gains from appreciation, and rental income.

3. Create a business: Starting your own business can help you earn money in a variety of ways. As a business owner, you can sell products or services to customers or clients, earn passive income through advertising, and even sell your business for a profit in the future.
